name: Nantucket Candy Cane - 1.50mm Carriage
description:
Nantuckets 1854 is offering “Nantucket Candy Cane” in a 1.50mm Carriage width. Chosen for its fine detailed quality, the 1.50mm Carriage Cane is smaller width that gives a fine detailed finished look to your basket. Ideal for many applications such as weaving a smaller lightship basket, weaving a contrasting lid on a friendship basket, or giving your Nantucket basket a refined woven presentation on a larger basket.

Nantuckets 1854 believes whether you are a professional or just getting started; choosing the best materials available will help you create a beautiful Nantucket basket. 

Happy weaving.

"Nantucket Candy Cane" 1.50mm Carriage comes in a 500 ft coil.

Other sizes available. Please inquire.
